body:
A function within a package that drives a default of 'x causes the error.

```
function automatic logic [15:0] copy_mask;
      input [15:0]  mask_in;
      input [1:0]   vsew;
      case(vsew[1:0])
	2'b00:                         copy_mask[15:0] =  mask_in[15:0];
	2'b01:   for(int i=0;i<16;i++) copy_mask[i]    =  mask_in[i[3:1]];
	2'b10:   for(int i=0;i<16;i++) copy_mask[i]    =  mask_in[i[3:2]];
	default:                       copy_mask[15:0] = 'x;
      endcase
   endfunction
```

%Error-UNSUPPORTED: : Unsupported: 4-state numbers in this context
   57 |  default: copy_mask[15:0] = 'x;
